{"tid":1048882,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"全部人行開！老豆！我決定咗！唔買GTR！","createTime":"2019-03-06T01:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T03:08:39.000Z","uid":13495,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"03d59e207b83363df78c1d6735ad86254677068b","tid":1048882,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:52:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">P牌仔向父借車　偕兩友大山遊車河　失控撞壆反肚冒煙</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨日(3月5日)深夜11時許，一輛掛有P牌私家車，沿大帽山荃錦公路往八鄉方向行駛，途至近蟾蜍石一個右彎時，突然失控越過對面行車線，再撼向通往扶輪山徑樓梯入口位置石壆，繼而反肚四輪朝天，同時冒煙。車上3名男子一度被困，消防接報到場將3人救出，分由兩輛救護車送往仁濟醫院治理。據悉，司機為一名年輕男子，借用父親的私家車，載同兩名友人遊車河，期間發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n警方正調查車禍原因。受事件影響，荃錦公路來回交通一度受阻。警方指，涉事司機姓葉(22歲)，頭部受傷；兩名姓黃(23歲)及姓李(24歲)男乘客，則分別手及腹受傷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/06/094956_a40ac9d18077454b219177104fc7500b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F06%2F094956_a40ac9d18077454b219177104fc7500b.png&h=6184b8d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/06/094957_02390f9ae499a3add8d92570008a5385.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F06%2F094957_02390f9ae499a3add8d92570008a5385.png&h=b92f2385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/302591/p%E7%89%8C%E4%BB%94%E5%90%91%E7%88%B6%E5%80%9F%E8%BB%8A-%E5%81%95%E5%85%A9%E5%8F%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%BD%E5%B1%B1%E9%81%8A%E8%BB%8A%E6%B2%B3-%E5%A4%B1%E6%8E%A7%E6%92%9E%E5%A3%86%E5%8F%8D%E8%82%9A%E5%86%92%E7%85%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F302591%2Fp%25E7%2589%258C%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%2590%2591%25E7%2588%25B6%25E5%2580%259F%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E5%2581%2595%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B8%25BD%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%25B2%25B3-%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2592%259E%25E5%25A3%2586%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%2582%259A%25E5%2586%2592%25E7%2585%2599&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXsls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=8cc88aaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/302591/p%E7%89%8C%E4%BB%94%E5%90%91%E7%88%B6%E5%80%9F%E8%BB%8A-%E5%81%95%E5%85%A9%E5%8F%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%BD%E5%B1%B1%E9%81%8A%E8%BB%8A%E6%B2%B3-%E5%A4%B1%E6%8E%A7%E6%92%9E%E5%A3%86%E5%8F%8D%E8%82%9A%E5%86%92%E7%85%99</a><br />\n<br />\n正如__ __個老豆話齋 跌低咗 自己起返身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935300080d8019001725df74bdc480eafabc8e64","tid":1048882,"uid":13495,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:53:28.000Z","msg":"老豆前晚又去左金旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/06/095327_4a5a06a6eed1d938385634e15c8da08b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F06%2F095327_4a5a06a6eed1d938385634e15c8da08b.png&h=6df9dae7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57a546828dbe36ec2b24ca48e1632ffc7a76acd3","tid":1048882,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:04:04.000Z","msg":"肯定係太多乘客太重先出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a1318cdd50cceef7efd513607bbcf9f8dd6a2b","tid":1048882,"uid":152141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:15:39.000Z","msg":"第一句講左自己避狗未"},{"pid":"c3901d3a90ed928bd84a8ab92caf713b6258a84d","tid":1048882,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:16:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b0749ba351cdc98175334a3cec901f8a769d4ba","tid":1048882,"uid":2898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:17:00.000Z","msg":"咁你當冇我呢個老豆啦"},{"pid":"23acea2b1903ef0f9bb726eb044b2816d01a3773","tid":1048882,"uid":32722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45a1318cdd50cceef